### UI Layer

#### [NEW] [theme.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/theme.py)
- `_build_stylesheet(tokens)` — single function generating full QSS
- `get_dark_stylesheet()` / `get_light_stylesheet()`
- `apply_theme(app, theme_name)` — sets global stylesheet
- SVG icon paths with forward-slash for Windows Qt compatibility

#### [NEW] [searchable_combo.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/searchable_combo.py)
