#### [NEW] [header_bar.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/header_bar.py)
- App title "SRT Chapter Splitter", version label, Settings button, Restart button

#### [NEW] [settings_dialog.py](file:///F:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/ui/settings_dialog.py)
- QDialog with QScrollArea
- **API Endpoints section**: dynamic add/remove endpoints (base_url, api_key masked, model, enable toggle)
